snippet.title: Eletta - 1 Minute of Early Gameplay
snippet.description:
A short demonstration of how the game mechanics work together in Eletta.
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3024120/Eletta/?utm_source=youtube_mv3

Explore an unfamiliar place filled with powerful enemies, advanced technology and scientific advancements in Eletta, an action game about a young girl looking for a way back home.
